# The `MipsFastISel.cpp` File Reference

<DoxygenPage pluginConfig={pluginConfig}>

This file defines the MIPS-specific support for the <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/fastisel">FastISel</a> class. <a href="#details">More...</a>

## Description {#details}

This file defines the MIPS-specific support for the <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/fastisel">FastISel</a> class.

Some of the target-specific code is generated by tablegen in the file MipsGenFastISel.inc, which is #included here.
